---

<section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-dark via-accent to-accent-glow"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.08) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.08) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"></div>

  <div class="container-site relative z-10 text-center">
    <p class="font-outfit text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-white/60 mb-6 reveal">
      Start Cooking
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-heading text-[var(--font-size-display)] text-white mb-6 reveal">
      今日の食卓を、特別に。
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-white/70 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 reveal">
      旬の食材が持つ本来の美味しさを引き出す、<br />プレミアムなレシピをお試しください。
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center reveal">
      <a href="/recipes/" class="btn-primary bg-white! text-primary! hover:shadow-[0_12px_32px_rgba(255,255,255,0.3)]">
        <span>レシピを探す</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/seasonal/" class="btn-outline border-white/30 text-white hover:border-white hover:text-white">
        四季の図鑑を見る
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
